1. *Toalet* je neophodan u svakoj kući. (The toilet is necessary in every house.)
2. On je otišao u *toalet*. (He went to the toilet.)
3. *Toalet* papir je potreban za higijenu. (Toilet paper is necessary for hygiene.)
4. *Toalet* je pun čudnih mirisa. (The toilet is full of strange smells.)
5. Unutrašnjost *toaleta* je elegantna. (The interior of the toilet is elegant.)